info.name: DNS TXT Record Detected
author: pdteam
info.description: A DNS TXT record was detected. The TXT record lets a domain admin leave notes on a DNS server.

request:
;; opcode: QUERY, status: NOERROR, id: 12124
;; flags: rd ad; QUERY: 1, ANSWER: 0, AUTHORITY: 0, ADDITIONAL: 1

;; OPT PSEUDOSECTION:
; EDNS: version 0; flags: ; udp: 4096

;; QUESTION SECTION:
;ants.gouv.fr.	IN	 TXT
response:
;; opcode: QUERY, status: NOERROR, id: 12124
;; flags: qr rd ra; QUERY: 1, ANSWER: 2, AUTHORITY: 0, ADDITIONAL: 1

;; OPT PSEUDOSECTION:
; EDNS: version 0; flags: ; udp: 1232

;; QUESTION SECTION:
;ants.gouv.fr.	IN	 TXT

;; ANSWER SECTION:
ants.gouv.fr.	3600	IN	TXT	"v=spf1 mx a ptr ip4:82.97.16.240/28 ip4:82.97.22.0/28 ip4:217.108.240.82 ip4:217.108.80.226 ip4:217.174.195.0/27 include:ppb.worldline.com ~all"
ants.gouv.fr.	3600	IN	TXT	"globalsign-domain-verification=XFixJjABQCa8I_qjv-wCpcrbx9DPYN4nVzULqSmhov"

info.name: NS Record Detection
author: pdteam

;; OPT PSEUDOSECTION:

;; opcode: QUERY, status: NOERROR, id: 48006

ants.gouv.fr.	3600	IN	NS	ns7.oleane.net.
